{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究杠杆平衡条件。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">动力</span>&times;动力臂<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">=</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阻力&times;阻力臂。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杠杆、钩码、弹簧测力计</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调节杠杆水平平衡；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在杠杆左侧悬挂一定质量钩码；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">右侧用弹簧测力计竖直向下拉，使杠杆处于平衡状态；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将力和力臂记录在表格中；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">保持钩码和弹簧测力计位置不变，改变钩码数量，观察弹簧测力计示数有何变化？将结果记录在表格中；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">6.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">保持钩码数量和位置不变，改变弹簧测力计位置，观察弹簧测力计示数有何变化？将结果记录在表格中；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">7.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">保持钩码的数量和弹簧测力计的位置不变，改变钩码位置，观察弹簧测力计示数有何变化？将结果记录在表格中。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">动力</span>&times;动力臂=阻力&times;阻力臂。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杠杆应水平位置平衡，这样所有的拉力均竖直向下，力臂为支点到力的作用点的距离，以便于力臂的测量。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}